The Arts Council is delighted to announce it has made awards totalling £33,000 during April to 7 community based arts projects across Northern Ireland as part of the #NationalLottery funded Small Grants programme. Recipients of funding include Tumble Circus who will develop and present a new Circus show for families at the MAC Belfast on 27 & 28 May. For further details visit artscouncil-ni.org

Beyond beer. The Tuborg Foundation supports volunteer communities within music, sports, education and other social initiatives. We created an identity that celebrates the people behind the fellowship through something as personal and unique as handwriting.⠀
To separate the foundation from the brew, we revisited the archives and chose a distinct red identity colour from one of the first beer labels. As a subtle reference to the Tuborg beer brand, we kept the logo iconic shape for a distinct, yet recognisable, logo for @tuborgfondet

Take Note ... What's important is just to give thanks to the Almighty for giving us another moment to number our days on earth. Death is certain !!! #MYBIRTHDAY ... 2017 is a year of which I entered consciously with strict calculation and constant reviewing of self activities . Going back January 1st I told my family this year isn't about buying cars , houses , phones , travels and shits . we don't have that goal , if it comes I did be glad own it .

Moving forward I want to build businesses , make impact , employ more people so they can transfer wealth to their family & contribute to the society .

fast forward May 2017 Im co-convener at Quorum Nigeria @quorumnigeria a social advocacy &  empowerment platform that allows every Nigerian to air their views on issues affecting their lives & the nation in general with the end goal of offering vital solutions using information Technology & Traditional media approach. 
I have successfully founded & co-owned a digital mobile startup that allows filmmakers / producers / photographers /events manager get easy access to choice location for their projects & gives all kind property owners both private & commercial the opportunity to monetize their homes filmlocations.com.ng 
To the glory of God we restructured our film production company 1705 Productions Ltd now its up & running again .All this in 5months with little or no funds .www.1705productions.com.ng 
The moral of today is to motivate myself & you out there looking for a way out .. just do it , a simple phone call or text massage changes life. 
Don't wait for big figures to start up , be creative and think of what you can do without money . #happybirthday #digitaltech #filmlocations #filmmakers #producers #techworld #startup #smes #africa #sillyconvalley #advertising #media #Family #dırector #funding
